data.title: Loan: Hebei: Zhangjiakou: Chicheng
data.meta_description: Loan: Hebei: Zhangjiakou: Chicheng data was reported at 9,793.690 RMB mn in Dec 2021. This records an increase from the previous number of 9,072.840 RMB mn for Dec 2020. Loan: Hebei: Zhangjiakou: Chicheng data is updated yearly, averaging 3,874.170 RMB mn (Median) from Dec 2004 to 2021, with 18 observations. The data reached an all-time high of 9,793.690 RMB mn in 2021 and a record low of 720.470 RMB mn in 2004. Loan: Hebei: Zhangjiakou: Chicheng data remains active status in CEIC and is reported by The People's Bank of China. The data is categorized under China Premium Database’s Money and Banking – Table CN.KG: Loan: County Level Region.
